296
0:16:33,467 --> 0:16:35,867
That means you've
got less customers.


297
0:16:35,867 --> 0:16:38,367
Businesses get fewer profits.


298
0:16:38,367 --> 0:16:40,133
They hire fewer workers.


299
0:16:40,133 --> 0:16:42,867
You go in a downward spiral.


300
0:16:42,867 --> 0:16:43,9
Wrong idea.


301
0:16:43,9 --> 0:16:48,533
Here is the good news: We
can solve this problem.


302
0:16:48,533 --> 0:16:52,7
All Congress needs to do is pass
a law that would prevent a tax


303
0:16:52,7 --> 0:16:58,133
hike on the first $250,000 of
