350
0:19:25,7 --> 0:19:28,7
the help that they
need through Medicaid.


351
0:19:28,7 --> 0:19:29,7
We're not going to do that.


352
0:19:29,7 --> 0:19:30,834
We're not going to
make that tradeoff.


353
0:19:30,834 --> 0:19:33,834
That's not going
to help us to grow.


354
0:19:33,834 --> 0:19:37,33
Our economic success has never
