355
0:19:37,33 --> 0:19:38,567
from the middle out.


356
0:19:38,567 --> 0:19:39,7
It comes from the bottom up.


357
0:19:39,7 --> 0:19:40,934
(applause)


358
0:19:40,934 --> 0:19:45,2
It comes from folks like you
working hard, and if you're


359
0:19:45,2 --> 0:19:47,667
working hard and you're
successful, then you become


360
0:19:47,667 --> 0:19:51,467
customers and
